{"tid":740383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首屆《全港青少年抖音》公開賽","createTime":"2018-07-13T00:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T06:35:31.000Z","uid":71543,"like":3,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8ebfdbe23e4655997371146a52b5c0ae5c5be7a2","tid":740383,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T00:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/081602_80d9166c297c756fdc48a49226dd08a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F081602_80d9166c297c756fdc48a49226dd08a6.jpg&h=38cfdf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比賽內容：<br />\n・短片內容必須切合「粵港澳大灣區」的主題。與粵港澳大灣區城市群發展建設相關的人文文化、社會民生、政經制度等課題均可。<br />\n<br />\n參賽資格：<br />\n・公開組：10歲以上本港青少年<br />\n・義工組：有志於從事義工服務的10至24歲本港青少年<br />\n<br />\n比賽形式：<br />\n・公開組：提交大會 一條自己製作的抖音音樂短視頻 。<br />\n・義工組：於社區教授一 位或多位不善於應用社交媒體的人士，如長者 等，並與之製作一條抖音音樂短視頻，提交予大會。<br />\n<br />\n報名費用全免❗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DigitalEyeHK/photos/a.158136307602100.39332.122446361171095/1749929285089453/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDigitalEyeHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.158136307602100.39332.122446361171095%2F1749929285089453%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=q%2F3aqDls715cMVn5yXnKLZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ff233c21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DigitalEyeHK/photos/a.158136307602100.39332.122446361171095/1749929285089453/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"072913ce77e9f4be633e6d3a2ce270498c2391b1","tid":740383,"uid":71543,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"今鋪真係我們一起學貓叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5912bb82365467e25f378a13029835fd9f9a85","tid":740383,"uid":71543,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"又大灣區又抖音又慶祝香港回歸祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/do